1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
ظآزWandering aloneظآز

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
ظآزWalking far by dusk-lit streetsظآز

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
ظآزYour eyes are as cold as cloudsظآز

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
ظآزFaintly coming into viewظآز

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
ظآزThe city lightsظآز

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
ظآزLit up that single momentظآز

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
ظآزI can't hide or stop missing youظآز

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
ظآزI can't forget those momentsظآز

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
ظآزLosing youظآز

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
ظآزLike the seasons in my memoryظآز

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
ظآزWithout winterظآز

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
ظآزWalking down the long, dark streetظآز

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
ظآزSnow will never fall againظآز

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
ظآزOur old story was tornظآز

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
ظآزInto scattered piecesظآز

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
ظآزReplaying every single sceneظآز

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
ظآزAfter you leftظآز

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
ظآزAs if our documentaryظآز

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
ظآزLost winterظآز

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
ظآزThe breeze speaks of good timesظآز

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
ظآزPure white devotionظآز

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
ظآزSend out a letterظآز

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
ظآزCarrying my longingظآز

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 9=

26
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,040
This...

27
00:01:34,710 --> 00:01:35,550
Tingxiao,

28
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,560
what do you mean?

29
00:01:37,070 --> 00:01:38,590
She's a traitor to both our families.

30
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,710
That's what I wanted.

31
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:41,880
You...

32
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:47,400
Are you covering for her?

33
00:01:47,590 --> 00:01:48,430
Chairman Lin,

34
00:01:49,243 --> 00:01:50,556
instead of telling me what to do,

35
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,870
think about cleaning up your own mess.

36
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,913
Do you really think no one knows

37
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,310
about your shady business?

38
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,560
While I'm still showing you
some respect,

39
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:01,960
take your people

40
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,450
and get out, now.

41
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,320
You...

42
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:08,270
You two.

43
00:02:08,910 --> 00:02:09,750
Fine.

44
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,030
Let's go.

45
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,910
Thanks for today.

46
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,680
This may be a mood killer,

47
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,673
but I still want to ask:

48
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,150
How much do you know

49
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:58,210
about the reclamation?

50
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:03,680
Only after coming back and taking over.

51
00:03:07,710 --> 00:03:09,030
Then do you blame me?

52
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:11,150
After all, the video I posted

53
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:13,630
did hurt your company's interests.

54
00:03:16,273 --> 00:03:17,466
I have no reason to blame you.

55
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,150
You just did the right thing.

56
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,030
Besides,

57
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,680
the Group's interests can't cross lines

58
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,840
or rest on other people's pain.

59
00:03:30,633 --> 00:03:31,819
But I should make this clear:

60
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:33,280
I did post the video,

61
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,150
but I wasn't the one who reported it.

62
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:38,150
The second I posted the video,

63
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,430
it was seized.

64
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,910
Too coincidental.

65
00:03:41,220 --> 00:03:42,090
I know.

66
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:45,080
Maybe Lu Jianchuan reported it
because he thought

67
00:03:45,236 --> 00:03:46,476
Lin Youqiang wanted to go solo.

68
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:49,360
I don't think so.

69
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:54,190
Who do you think this person is?

70
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:01,030
Maybe someone

71
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,870
who wants the truth

72
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:05,750
out in the open just like you.

73
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:13,750
If only

74
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,160
I weren't your sister-in-law.

75
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,950
If I weren't Lin Zhi'er,

76
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:25,350
what do you think

77
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,510
we'd be to each other now?

78
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,720
If you weren't Lin Zhi'er,

79
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,950
I wouldn't have to suffer

80
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:38,070
or keep finding reasons to avoid you.

81
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,680
Then I can stand by your side openly

82
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,400
and protect you.

83
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,890
ظآزWalking through storms and duskظآز

84
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,870
Here's a secret.

85
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,630
I'm not Lin Zhi'er.

86
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:58,870
I have a secret too.

87
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:01,350
ظآزSitting with my shadow ظآز

88
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,240
I've known your secret all along,

89
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,840
Wen Yan.

90
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,080
You...

91
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,390
You've known all along?

92
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,920
No wonder

93
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,270
you've been getting pretty bold lately.

94
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,000
Have I?

95
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:24,710
Haven't you?

96
00:05:25,330 --> 00:05:28,760
ظآزI can walk through storms
and dusk aloneظآز

97
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:32,180
ظآزAnd calmly take the warmth you offerظآز

98
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:34,900
ظآزNot sacrificing for anyoneظآز

99
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:38,860
ظآزNot made whole by anyoneظآز

100
00:05:39,550 --> 00:05:43,760
ظآزI've learned to stop waitingظآز

101
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:47,880
ظآزOnly then did I dare keep you for lifeظآز

102
00:06:15,060 --> 00:06:16,780
(Bai)

103
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,850
Okay, got it.

104
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:22,150
I'll be right there.

105
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,510
It's urgent.

106
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,520
Well...

107
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,320
Go ahead.

108
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,560
I'm leaving.

109
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:47,240
You like him?

110
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,430
Is it that obvious?

111
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,400
No.

112
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,680
Not as obvious as him.

113
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,830
The studio got trashed.

114
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,560
What are you going to do now?

115
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:08,600
I can't stay here anymore.

116
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,000
I need a new place.

117
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,760
Aunt Hui,

118
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,880
thank you

119
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,040
for looking after me

120
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,400
all this time

121
00:07:18,870 --> 00:07:20,720
and telling me so much
about Lianxin Island.

122
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,560
But from now on,

123
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,510
we can't be neighbors anymore.

124
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,160
Don't talk like we're strangers.

125
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,360
Before you move away,

126
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:33,240
could you go to Lianxin Island with me?

127
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,510
The island's been changed.

128
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,640
Actually,

129
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:58,830
I didn't tell you
about the details between Lin

130
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,870
and the Village Chief.

131
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:04,240
After the Village Chief's daughter
was cast aside,

132
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,120
she soon found out

133
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:08,000
she was carrying Lin's child.

134
00:08:09,870 --> 00:08:11,430
She went to the city to find him,

135
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:13,870
only to learn he was already married.

136
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:15,750
The Village Chief

137
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,000
went to report it,

138
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:20,160
but Lu Jianchuan
used his pull to bury it.

139
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,270
Lin feared they'd make more trouble,

140
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,040
so he took away

141
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,040
their newborn girl.

142
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,920
So,

143
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,280
that child

144
00:08:36,910 --> 00:08:37,870
was Lin Zhi'er?

145
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:50,150
Wasn't the island seized?

146
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,750
Why is there still construction
over there?

147
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,670
Aunt Hui, head back first.

148
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,930
I'll go take a look.

149
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,800
Okay.

150
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,800
Be careful.

151
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:16,840
Come on, move faster.

152
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:18,720
This section must be done by dawn.

153
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,870
- Okay.
- Okay.

154
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:22,030
Working by day makes too much noise.

155
00:09:22,173 --> 00:09:23,399
Have them speed it up at night.

156
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:25,030
Bai?

157
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,510
I'll go check first.

158
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,920
Okay.

159
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,080
What are you doing?

160
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,390
Bai!

161
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:38,710
Bai!

162
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:41,990
Let her go.

163
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:54,870
Get back to work.

164
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:55,870
Yes.

165
00:09:57,750 --> 00:09:58,590
Lu Tingxiao,

166
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,320
why are you here?

167
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,080
So,

168
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,480
you told them to start illegally?

169
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,920
Yes.

170
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:18,320
Do you know that's against the law?

171
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:21,710
I do.

172
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,600
I'm really disappointed in you.

173
00:10:29,730 --> 00:10:30,710
Don't get the wrong idea.

174
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,440
Mr. Lu didn't do this
to help Lu Jianchuan.

175
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:37,150
He did it to blow this whole thing up,

176
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,080
so the project gets shut down for good.

177
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,040
What do you mean?

178
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:47,510
You've been wondering who my boss is.

179
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,600
Mr. Lu is my boss.

180
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:52,360
He reported

181
00:10:52,856 --> 00:10:53,796
the illegal reclamation.

182
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:56,510
He set this up while overseas.

183
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,160
He knew Lu Jianchuan

184
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,686
would raise funds with this project,

185
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,200
so he jumped right in.

186
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:03,360
He had me blend in with the investors

187
00:11:03,603 --> 00:11:04,836
and stir investors to pull out.

188
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,480
What happened that day

189
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,720
was part of his plan

190
00:11:08,270 --> 00:11:09,670
to kick Xu Shulin and her brother

191
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:10,790
out of the game

192
00:11:11,550 --> 00:11:13,030
and take power fair and square.

193
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,600
After he took power,

194
00:11:14,989 --> 00:11:16,675
he kept digging for dirt
on Lu Jianchuan.

195
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:30,820
(Lianxin Island:
Illegal Land Reclamation)

196
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,960
That led to the report and seizure.

197
00:11:37,910 --> 00:11:38,750
Of course,

198
00:11:39,196 --> 00:11:40,429
the seizure was just the start.

199
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,790
Once the illegal construction blows up,

200
00:11:43,373 --> 00:11:44,746
even Lu Jianchuan won't contain it.

201
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:50,510
So,

202
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,750
you started the construction

203
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:53,970
to blow this whole thing up

204
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:56,440
and bring down Lu Jianchuan
and Xu Shulin,

205
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,840
so you could take back Luzhou Group

206
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,510
and get payback for your mom.

207
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,120
They were wrong first.

208
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,440
I couldn't let them go easily.

209
00:12:13,550 --> 00:12:14,390
Wen Yan,

210
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,080
I know you got into the Lu family

211
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,790
to look into Lianxin Island.

212
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:21,150
But can you promise me

213
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:23,200
not to risk it alone again?

214
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,560
I can't even imagine

215
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:26,750
what would've happened today

216
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:27,840
if the one you met here

217
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,200
hadn't been me.

218
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,270
We're after the same thing.

219
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,280
I can help you.

220
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:36,750
Okay.

221
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,480
ظآزThis doorظآز

222
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:07,630
ظآزLets in the sky outsideظآز

223
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:11,670
ظآزWith a voice even lighterظآز

224
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:14,480
ظآزThan how you just greeted meظآز

225
00:13:14,930 --> 00:13:16,300
ظآزI know nowظآز

226
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:21,510
ظآزWhat the chill in my body meansظآز

227
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:24,730
ظآزThe moment salt hits the woundظآز

228
00:13:24,930 --> 00:13:28,350
ظآزMy heart still beats so naivelyظآز

229
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:31,510
ظآزTo completeظآز

230
00:13:31,970 --> 00:13:35,720
ظآزA joy that needs no brave pretenseظآز

231
00:13:35,860 --> 00:13:38,360
ظآزHow cruel sincerity can beظآز

232
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:42,050
ظآزLike a door with no keyظآز

233
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:44,680
ظآزMaybe you just passed byظآز

234
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:48,260
ظآزThe tears in my eyesظآز

235
00:13:48,970 --> 00:13:51,520
ظآزYou looked like you had nothing to sayظآز

236
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,260
ظآزThen got so good at being coldظآز

237
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:56,100
ظآزThat's why a smile feels so preciousظآز

238
00:13:56,310 --> 00:13:58,400
ظآزMaybe you just passed byظآز

239
00:13:58,550 --> 00:14:02,880
ظآزThe tears burned into my heartظآز

240
00:14:03,260 --> 00:14:05,550
ظآزLet's say silence was just for showظآز

241
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:10,220
ظآزEven if I've grown another yearظآز
